{"tid":430120,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想分手又開唔到口","createTime":"2017-10-09T13:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T04:15:42.000Z","uid":77949,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b56c2504b54987c75e33eadb6cbe54023eb189","tid":430120,"uid":77949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得繼續行落去到結婚既話會後悔<br />\n<br />\n但係又唔捨得呢四年幾既感情...<br />\n<br />\n唉  可能我第一次拍拖  無經驗<br />\n<br />\n一諗起講完之後大家都傷心既情景就唔敢講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    是咪好廢"},{"pid":"fe051b3f3fbdbb8ef9e25db2ababc59c47ea2bfe","tid":430120,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"咩原因想分？"},{"pid":"5c80db352e18b04ff317548093b7cdd173f7549f","tid":430120,"uid":92963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T13:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得繼續行落去到結婚既話會後悔<br />\n<br />\n但係又唔捨得呢四年幾既感情...<br />\n<br />\n唉  可能我第一次拍拖  無經驗<br />\n<br />\n一諗起講完之後大家都傷心既情景就唔敢講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    是咪好廢</blockquote><br />\n同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4deb6131ca8b1a07d73c2f9eb462293da51a490","tid":430120,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"咩事想分 ？"},{"pid":"856bcc0c78587b07c06b7c4d729067523ef76d1c","tid":430120,"uid":77949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩原因想分？</blockquote><br />\n好多好細微既野搞到覺得遲D就算行落去都會辛苦<br />\n<br />\n可能我岩岩踏足社會, 返工要博D搞到自己唔太夠時間用<br />\n<br />\n有時收工傾電話會好攰,會開口話有D想訓<br />\n<br />\n但佢就唔太了解我既情況咁成日詐型話我掛住訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得佢唔太識體諒我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都明自己可能擺少左時間係佢度 加上佢重在學  可能唔明返工既辛苦之處<br />\n<br />\n但有時因為咁樣又要勞心勞力去哄返佢覺得好攰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然唔止咁少, 以上只係其中一例  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實四年幾以黎, 大家既習性都似乎唔太夾  當然大家都有努力去改去磨合<br />\n<br />\n但硬係隔一陣就會打回原形  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f5445e9c31cb6dfe46efacaa49f4ba7df13875","tid":430120,"uid":77949,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得繼續行落去到結婚既話會後悔<br />\n<br />\n但係又唔捨得呢四年幾既感情...<br />\n<br />\n唉  可能我第一次拍拖  無經驗<br />\n<br />\n一諗起講完之後大家都傷心既情景就唔敢講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    是咪好廢</blockquote><br />\n同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57e7e64857aa1a3a9bc7dd741532ff5448922a6","tid":430120,"uid":73909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:55:22.000Z","msg":"你已經浪費咗四年時間 你仲想一直浪費落去？"},{"pid":"8c72c60fbd70a5b6080fdbf3a10bffbddeedb2ed","tid":430120,"uid":129877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:57:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩原因想分？</blockquote><br />\n好多好細微既野搞到覺得遲D就算行落去都會辛苦<br />\n<br />\n可能我岩岩踏足社會, 返工要博D搞到自己唔太夠時間用<br />\n<br />\n有時收工傾電話會好攰,會開口話有D想訓<br />\n<br />\n但佢就唔太了解我既情況咁成日詐型話我掛住訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得佢唔太識體諒我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都明自己可能擺少左時間係佢度 加上佢重在學  可能唔明返工既辛苦之處<br />\n<br />\n但有時因為咁樣又要勞心勞力去哄返佢覺得好攰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然唔止咁少, 以上只係其中一例  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實四年幾以黎, 大家既習性都似乎唔太夾  當然大家都有努力去改去磨合<br />\n<br />\n但硬係隔一陣就會打回原形  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /